@startuml Sequence - Pelunasan Hutang
actor "Admin Toko" as Admin
participant "UI" as UI
participant "Debts API" as DebtAPI
participant "Sales API" as SaleAPI
participant "Debt Service" as Service
database "Database" as DB

== Skenario 1: Pelunasan Mandiri ==
Admin -> UI : Masukkan nominal & klik bayar
UI -> DebtAPI : POST /api/debts/{id}/payment
activate DebtAPI
DebtAPI -> Service : processDebtPayment()
activate Service
Service -> DB : Update Data Hutang
DB --> Service : OK
Service --> DebtAPI : Result
deactivate Service
DebtAPI --> UI : 200 OK
UI --> Admin : Notif Sukses

== Skenario 2: Pelunasan via Penjualan (Otomatis) ==
Admin -> UI : Proses Penjualan (Metode Cash + Surplus)
UI -> SaleAPI : POST /api/sales
activate SaleAPI
SaleAPI -> DB : Simpan Transaksi Penjualan
SaleAPI -> DB : Cek Hutang Aktif Pelanggan
DB --> SaleAPI : Daftar Hutang
loop Tiap Hutang (selama ada surplus)
    SaleAPI -> Service : processDebtPayment()
    activate Service
    Service -> DB : Update Data Hutang
    DB --> Service : OK
    Service --> SaleAPI : Result
    deactivate Service
end
SaleAPI --> UI : 200 OK (Invoice + Info Pelunasan)
UI --> Admin : Notif Sukses & Struk Pelunasan
deactivate SaleAPI

@enduml
